You have 96 degrees Celsius,

00:02:33.813 --> 00:02:35.389
so this is almost at the boiling point.

00:02:35.389 --> 00:02:36.645
So it's quite hot,

00:02:36.645 --> 00:02:40.213
and that separates the two strands.

00:02:40.213 --> 00:02:41.506
- [Voiceover] Precisely.

00:02:41.506 --> 00:02:43.349
- [Voiceover] And so
once they're separated,

00:02:43.349 --> 00:02:45.425
