You'd put whatever your
initial DNA sample is in there,

00:03:41.408 --> 00:03:43.792
and once again it's a very small amount,

00:03:43.792 --> 00:03:45.306
you'd put a lot of that primer,

00:03:45.306 --> 00:03:47.155
so you'd want to put
that in a lot of surplus,

00:03:47.155 --> 00:03:49.832
so let me do that in this magenta color.

