00:03:55.256 --> 00:03:56.195
- [Voiceover] It would look like...

00:03:56.195 --> 00:03:58.012
But for visualization,
you'd put a lot of primer,

00:03:58.012 --> 00:04:01.251
and so you heat it up,
the DNA strands separate,

00:04:01.251 --> 00:04:03.136
