00:05:38.890 --> 00:05:40.244
you don't have an enzyme to do it

00:05:40.244 --> 00:05:41.578
the way you might in a cell,

00:05:41.578 --> 00:05:43.250
so heat does the trick.

00:05:43.250 --> 00:05:44.305
- [Voiceover] Okay, so I get it.

00:05:44.305 --> 00:05:45.564
So this is one step,

00:05:45.564 --> 00:05:49.658
I'm getting at least the
